headline: 'Fossil vs Seiko: Fashion Watches vs Horological Heritage',
metaDesc: 'Fossil vs Seiko compared. Fashion-forward design vs Japanese horological mastery. Movements, build quality, value retention, and which brand is actually worth buying.',
